      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Judah and Jerusalem.—So 2Chronicles 20:27. Jerusalem is thus mentioned side by side with the country, as being by far the most important part of it. (See also the headings of Isaiah 1, 2)",
        "children": [
          {
            "element": "span",
