            "text": "2Chronicles 4:9",
            "children": []
          },
          {
            "element": "span",
            "class": "",
            "text": ") or outer court of the Temple, in which the people assembled. Jehoshaphat stood facing the people, in front of the entrance to the Court of the Priests. Perhaps the court was called ",
